# Keep the build context lean and the in-image install clean (no host artefacts leaking in).
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.git
.github
logs
*.log
**/dist
**/.next
coverage
**/coverage
.archon/state
.archon/.env
scratchpad
# Large demo renders aren't needed at runtime (the demo *.jsonl ARE — keep them).
demo/*.png
